# Fastmail IMAP sync via mbsync
# Requires an App Password from Fastmail:
# Settings → Privacy & Security → App Passwords
#
# Store password in macOS Keychain (run once):
#   security add-internet-password -s imap.fastmail.com -a ehouse@fastmail.com -w

IMAPAccount fastmail
Host imap.fastmail.com
Port 993
User ehouse@fastmail.com
PassCmd "security find-internet-password -s imap.fastmail.com -a ehouse@fastmail.com -w"
TLSType IMAPS
AuthMechs LOGIN

IMAPStore fastmail-remote
Account fastmail

MaildirStore fastmail-local
SubFolders Verbatim
Path ~/Mail/fastmail/
Inbox ~/Mail/fastmail/Inbox

Channel fastmail
Far :fastmail-remote:
Near :fastmail-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
